 {"id":"jeffrey_emanuel_personal_site-r6r","title":"Create comprehensive content validation tests for content.ts","description":"## What
Create a test file that validates the integrity, consistency, and correctness of all data in lib/content.ts. These tests ensure our project additions don't introduce errors and maintain quality standards.

## Why
- Catch errors early before they reach production
- Ensure all required fields are present
- Prevent duplicate entries
- Validate URLs are properly formatted
- Ensure consistent tag usage across projects
- Verify badge format consistency
